data.description: Fort Myers Beach is a one-of-a-kind Island community comprised of 7 miles of unadulterated white sugar sand beaches . Fairview isles is a canal front community with deeded beach access and No mandatory HOA dues ! This home is situated just seconds to the back bay and minutes to the Gulf of Mexico on the widest intersecting canal on Fort Myers Beach in the nicest subdivision on FMB . The home has been totally remediated post Ian and ready for remodel - all the hard work has been done for you , all that's left is for you to choose how the home should be finished and enjoyed . The History of the island spans back to over 2000 years ! From Indians and Pirates to artists and party goers alike this island is alive and has plans for the future - will you be a part of it or left watching from the sidelines ? All of those ingredients put together gives you a once in a lifetime recipe for success . Design your future and future home and reserve your page in FMB history .
